exceptions.exn: In environment R : nat -> nat -> Set H0 : forall n : nat, R 0 n H1 : forall n : nat, R (S n) 0 H2 : forall n m : nat, R n m -> R (S n) (S m) Unable to unify "nat -> nat -> Set" with "nat -> nat -> Prop".
Applied theorem does not have enough premises.

original: intros R H0 H1 H2. apply PeanoNat.Nat.double_induction. - apply H0. - apply H1. - apply H2.
